-- Test on PI.PERFRMOACTIONS = Y to prevent starts of GB206 by mistake with
... set TRUE if info has to be written to joblog which tables are cleaned up,
can be used for testing purposes
-- Cleaup tables which are defined in TCDE
-- Trigger to check if there's a row defined in TCDE where no cleanup
task exists, in this case a row is written to job log

ExpSyntax.val: 'There is no task defined in GB206 for table'&' '&Trim ({0,1})

SQL_STMT_U.val: delete from :1/CAPI where not(exists(select * from :1/CADI where CADI_NO = CAPI_CADI_NO))
delete from :1/DLIT where not(exists(select * from :1/DLIJ where DLIJ_NO = DLIT_RUNNUMBER))
delete from :1/DLIN where not(exists(select * from :1/DLIT where DLIT_NO = DLIN_DLIT_NO))
delete from :1/DUNI where not(exists(select * from :1/DUNL where DUNL_ID = DUNI_DUNL_ID))
delete from :1/EHR1 where not(exists(select * from :1/EUHR where EUHR_REQID = EHR1_REQID))
delete from :1/EHR2 where not(exists(select * from :1/EUHR where EUHR_REQID = EHR2_REQID))
delete from :1/EHR3 where not(exists(select * from :1/EUHR where EUHR_REQID = EHR3_REQID))
delete from :1/IBYH where IBYH_DATEBUYING < ':2' and not(exists(select * from :1/INVA where INVA_NO = IBYH_NO))
delete from :1/NFIB where exists(select * from :1/NFIR where NFIR_NO = NFIB_NFIR_NO and NFIR_DATE < ':2')
delete from :1/NFIN where exists(select * from :1/NFIR where NFIR_NO = NFIN_NFIR_NO and NFIR_DATE < ':2')
delete from :1/NFIA where exists(select * from :1/NFIR where NFIR_NO = NFIA_NFIR_NO and NFIR_DATE < ':2')
delete from :1/SCHI where exists(select * from :1/SCHT where SCHT_NO = SCHI_SCHT_NO and SCHT_SCHEDDATERECV < ':2')
delete from :1/SCTM where exists(select * from :1/SCHT where SCHT_NO = SCTM_SCHT_NO and SCHT_SCHEDDATERECV < ':2')
delete from :1/SIIC where not(exists(select * from :1/STIC where STIC_ID = SIIC_STIC_ID))
delete from :1/SCIC where not(exists(select * from :1/STIC where STIC_ID = SCIC_STIC_ID))
delete from :1/TPIR where not(exists(select * from :1/TPIJ where TPIJ_RUNNUMBER = TPIR_RUNNUMBER))
delete from :1/TPIB where not(exists(select * from :1/TPIJ where TPIJ_RUNNUMBER = TPIB_RUNNUMBER))
delete from :1/DBHS where upper(trim(DBHS_VALUE_NEW)) = upper(trim(DBHS_VALUE_OLD)) and DBHS_DATE < ':2' and DBHS_USRIDAPPROVAL = ''
delete from :1/DCRM where DCRM_NOTICE is null and DCRM_DATE < ':2'
select BCNB_ADMNO, BCNB_LEDG_NO from :1/BCNB where BCNB_VALUEDATE < ':2' group by BCNB_ADMNO, BCNB_LEDG_NO
delete from :1/BCNB where BCNB_ADMNO = :2 and BCNB_LEDG_NO = :3 and BCNB_VALUEDATE < ':4'
select cast (sum (BCNB_CHANGESNETBALANCE) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/BCNB where BCNB_ADMNO = :2 and BCNB_LEDG_NO = :3 and BCNB_VALUEDATE < ':4'

select LGCD_ADMNO, LGCD_LDGR_NO, max(LGCD_LGCH_ID), (select cast (sum (b.LGCD_AMOUNTDEBITH) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/LGCD b where b.LGCD_DATE < ':2' and b.LGCD_ADMNO = LGCD_ADMNO and b.LGCD_LDGR_NO = LGCD_LDGR_NO), (select cast (sum (c.LGCD_AMOUNTCREDITH) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/LGCD c where c.LGCD_DATE < ':2' and c.LGCD_ADMNO = LGCD_ADMNO and c.LGCD_LDGR_NO = LGCD_LDGR_NO) from :1/LGCD where LGCD_DATE < ':2' group by LGCD_ADMNO, LGCD_LDGR_NO
delete from :1/LGCD where LGCD_ADMNO = :2 and LGCD_LDGR_NO = :3 and LGCD_DATE < ':4'

select LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO, LGCC_LDGR_NO, LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO, LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO, max(LGCC_LGCD_LGCH_ID), (select cast (sum (b.LGCC_AMOUNTH) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/LGCC b where b.LGCC_DATE < ':2' and b.LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO = LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO and b.LGCC_LDGR_NO = LGCC_LDGR_NO and b.LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO and b.LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO), (select cast (sum (c.LGCC_AMOUNTC) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/LGCC c where c.LGCC_DATE < ':2' and c.LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO = LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO and c.LGCC_LDGR_NO = LGCC_LDGR_NO and c.LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO and c.LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO) from :1/LGCC where LGCC_DATE < ':2' group by LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO, LGCC_LDGR_NO, LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO, LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO
delete from :1/LGCC where LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO = :2 and LGCC_LDGR_NO = :3 and LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :4 and LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :5 and LGCC_DATE < ':6'
delete from :1/CRRC where not(exists(select * from :1/CRRR where CRRR_NO = CRRC_CRRR_NO))
delete from :1/CRRD where not(exists(select * from :1/CRRR where CRRR_NO = CRRD_CRRR_NO))
delete from :1/CRRI where not(exists(select * from :1/CRRR where CRRR_NO = CRRI_CRRR_NO))
delete from :1/TUPD where not(exists(select * from :1/TUPH where TUPH_NO = TUPD_TUPH_NO))
